def my_func(input1: str, input2: str):
    indices = []
    input1_length = len(input1)
    input2_length = len(input2)
    limit = input1_length - input2_length + 1
    for i in range(limit):
        if input1[i:i+input2_length] == input2:
            indices.append(i)
    return indices
